body.description: Product Description Tampax Tampons cardboard applicator comes with Anti-Slip Grip for easier insertion. The absorbent core fits your unique shape, and the LeakGuard skirt helps stop leaks before they happen. And they come with a strong, durable wrapper for safe storage. You’ll also love Always Ultra Thin Pads and Always Dri-Liners. From the Manufacturer Tampax tampons flushable cardboard applicator comes with Anti-Slip Grip™ for easier insertion. The absorbent core fits your unique shape and the LeakGuard™ skirt helps stop leaks before they happen. And they come with a strong, durable wrapper for safe storage. You'll also love Always Ultra Thin Pads and Always Dri-Liners.FeaturesAccessoriesTAMPAX Flushable Cardboard FAQsWhat’s special about Tampax Flushable Cardboard?Thanks to FormFit™, Tampax Flushable Cardboard tampons gently expand to fit your unique shape. In addition, the LeakGuard® Skirt helps stop leaks before they happen. And Flushable Cardboard’s Anti-Slip Grip™ makes holding and inserting the tampon super easy.Can I flush the entire thing?While the wrapper and applicator are flushable, we recommend that the tampon be disposed of in the trash.What are Tampax Flushable Cardboard tampons made out of?They're made from cotton, rayon, polyester, polypropylene, polyethylene, fiber finishes.Comparison Chart

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cheap and efficient!
reviews.reviewText: Plain and simple, they work. No fancy pink plastic, and nothing to clog the toilet. Cost effective and efficient, there is no need to use any other brand.
